#.vscode/

# Flutter/Dart/Pub related
**/doc/api/
**/ios/Flutter/.last_build_id
.dart_tool/
.flutter-plugins-dependencies
.pub-cache/
.pub/
/build/
/coverage/

# Symbolication related
app.*.symbols

# Obfuscation related
app.*.map.json

# Android Studio will place build artifacts here
/android/app/debug
/android/app/profile
/android/app/release

# Release signing keystore (never commit — use GitHub secret for CI)
/android/app/upload-keystore.jks

# FlutterFire auto-generated config (contains Firebase client API keys)
# Android reads google-services.json directly at build time (generated from secret in CI).
/lib/firebase_options.dart
/android/app/google-services.json
